  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 88d55c3b1e26d7846b05368c30de55bb, type: 3}
  description: "Th\xE1i Nguy\xEAn l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng Trung
    du v\xE0 mi\u1EC1n n\xFAi B\u1EAFc B\u1ED9 \u1EDF ph\xEDa B\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t
    Nam. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 m\u1ED9t trung t\xE2m kinh t\u1EBF, gi\xE1o d\u1EE5c v\xE0
    c\xF4ng nghi\u1EC7p quan tr\u1ECDng c\u1EE7a khu v\u1EF1c. Trung t\xE2m c\u1EE7a
    t\u1EC9nh l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Th\xE1i Nguy\xEAn. T\u1EC9nh c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u
    \u0111\u1ECBa danh n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt nh\u01B0 H\u1ED3 N\xFAi C\u1ED1c v\xE0 Khu
    di t\xEDch ATK \u0110\u1ECBnh H\xF3a.\n\nTh\xE1i Nguy\xEAn n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng
    v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EA3n, \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t l\xE0 Ch\xE8
    T\xE2n C\u01B0\u01A1ng \u2013 m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng lo\u1EA1i ch\xE8 ngon
    v\xE0 n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng nh\u1EA5t Vi\u1EC7t Nam. Ngo\xE0i ra c\xF2n c\xF3 c\xE1c
    m\xF3n \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EA3n nh\u01B0 B\xE1nh ch\u01B0ng B\u1EDD \u0110\u1EADu
    v\xE0 c\xE1c s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m t\u1EEB ch\xE8.\n\nV\u1EC1 v\u0103n h\xF3a, Th\xE1i
    Nguy\xEAn l\xE0 n\u01A1i sinh s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a nhi\u1EC1u d\xE2n t\u1ED9c nh\u01B0
    T\xE0y, N\xF9ng, Dao, S\xE1n D\xECu v\u1EDBi \u0111\u1EDDi s\u1ED1ng v\u0103n
    h\xF3a \u0111a d\u1EA1ng. C\xE1c l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng, l\xE0n
    \u0111i\u1EC7u d\xE2n ca v\xE0 phong t\u1EE5c t\u1EADp qu\xE1n c\u1EE7a c\xE1c
    d\xE2n t\u1ED9c \u0111\xE3 t\u1EA1o n\xEAn b\u1EA3n s\u1EAFc v\u0103n h\xF3a
    \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng c\u1EE7a v\xF9ng trung du v\xE0 mi\u1EC1n n\xFAi B\u1EAFc
    B\u1ED9."
  desSatNhap: "T\u1EEB ng\xE0y 1/7/2025, t\u1EC9nh B\u1EAFc K\u1EA1n ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c
    s\xE1p nh\u1EADp v\xE0o t\u1EC9nh Th\xE1i Nguy\xEAn theo Ngh\u1ECB quy\u1EBFt
    202/2025/QH15, t\u1EA1o n\xEAn \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh m\u1EDBi
    mang t\xEAn Th\xE1i Nguy\xEAn. T\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi c\xF3 di\u1EC7n t\xEDch tr\xEAn
    8.300 km\xB2 v\xE0 d\xE2n s\u1ED1 g\u1EA7n 1,8 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, t\u1EADp
    trung ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n c\xF4ng nghi\u1EC7p v\u1EEFng ch\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a Th\xE1i
    Nguy\xEAn k\u1EBFt h\u1EE3p ti\u1EC1m n\u0103ng du l\u1ECBch, n\xF4ng nghi\u1EC7p
    c\u1EE7a B\u1EAFc K\u1EA1n."
